<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="perfectly-adv">perfectly <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'pɜːfɪktli/    美 /'pɜːrfɪktli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>非常；十分；完全地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I found a dress that suited me perfectly. 
我找了一件非常适合我的衣服。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 2</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Do you understand? 
你明白吗？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>— Perfectly. 
完全明白。</p></div></div>